    <node id="Periarticular Erosions">
      <data key="d0">Periarticular Erosions</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Periarticular Erosions

Periarticular erosions are bone erosions that occur around the joints and are revealed through X-ray imaging. These erosions represent a form of joint damage characterized by the loss or degradation of bone tissue in the areas immediately surrounding the joint structures. The condition is identifiable on radiographic imaging across multiple anatomical locations throughout the body.

Periarticular erosions have been documented in various joint locations, including the knee joint, shoulder joint, wrist, metacarpophalangeal joints (MCPs), and spinal joints. In the knee, bone erosions are observed around the joint on X-ray imaging. Similarly, erosions can be identified in the shoulder joint area and the wrist and MCP joints. The spine represents another significant site where periarticular erosions are commonly observed on X-ray imaging, indicating bone damage around the spinal joints.

X-ray imaging serves as the primary diagnostic tool for detecting and evaluating periarticular erosions. The radiographic findings reveal the extent and location of bone erosions surrounding the affected joints, providing clinicians with essential information regarding the degree of joint damage present. The presence of periarticular erosions on imaging studies indicates progressive joint pathology and structural deterioration of the bones adjacent to the joint margins.&lt;SEP&gt;Periarticular erosions are bone erosions around the joint detected on shoulder X-ray.&lt;SEP&gt;Bone erosions observed around the knee joint on X-ray imaging.&lt;SEP&gt;Bone erosions around the joints observed on X-ray of the wrist and MCPs.&lt;SEP&gt;Bone erosions around the joint margins detected on X-ray imaging, a characteristic finding of rheumatoid arthritis.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-b6969a3f3abe42a30b2b43bfafceacaa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-91f2e17beb9f3d24b9faa9059ed6acae&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c49c05a874ce6761c157c4e35dd9903b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-47645b674af4f2a88a64e49657a83073&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c1de22df34c77d7bc601fa40ded28a01&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-858effb6f3bd62fa4b2171b7a13e1257&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e78b4d015419c364789de541e7d7c770&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b2c623dc26c99ebd3a6caf0a7b69babb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-43ac57a7d8c6d0fe3f3c2007ee0bfd6c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c8a8e6a29e85b55ab54a20a5f904ef16&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c81af782e89b002c04a944dc0cea584&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d745ec6e17e6c423c81b61841434f2ce</data>
