    <node id="Primary CNS Lymphoma">
      <data key="d0">Primary CNS Lymphoma</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">A neurological condition diagnosed in the patient, characterized by malignant lymphoma of the central nervous system.&lt;SEP&gt;The diagnosis determined for the patient, representing a malignancy of the central nervous system.&lt;SEP&gt;A malignant condition affecting the central nervous system, diagnosed in the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;A cancer of lymphoid tissue in the central nervous system, diagnosed in the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;The diagnosed malignant condition affecting the central nervous system in the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;A neurological condition diagnosed in the patient, characterized by ring-enhancing lesion on MRI brain and positive Kernig's sign with hyperreflexia on examination.&lt;SEP&gt;A malignant cancer of the central nervous system diagnosed in the patient.</data>
