    <node id="Focal Weakness">
      <data key="d0">Focal Weakness</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Focal Weakness is a neurological symptom characterized by the sudden onset of loss of strength or motor function in specific, localized areas of the body. This symptom presents as a localized reduction in muscle power affecting particular body regions rather than generalized weakness throughout the body. The symptom typically manifests abruptly, with the affected areas experiencing diminished motor function and strength.

Focal Weakness is commonly observed in clinical presentations where patients experience lateralized neurological deficits. In particular, focal weakness may present as left-sided hemiplegia, a condition involving sudden onset loss of motor function affecting the left side of the body. The symptom is recognized as a significant neurological finding that indicates localized damage or dysfunction in the nervous system affecting motor control in specific anatomical regions.&lt;SEP&gt;Sudden onset of localized muscle weakness experienced by the patient as a primary symptom.&lt;SEP&gt;Sudden onset symptom characterized by localized muscle weakness observed in the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;Neurological symptom presented by the patient with sudden onset.&lt;SEP&gt;A neurological symptom characterized by sudden onset muscle weakness in a localized area, presented by the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;Focal weakness is a neurological symptom characterized by loss of strength in a specific area or region of the body.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-571ddc4aa63fdf4b9d03942b5048b279&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce7467c36645566972e9f92c5fea2ee8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1911d102d00d5197ec74e282f36fbad9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4fd7d8854cca43bc54c0fae9bacd07a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d21fe1428431fa9900c5bdf9740d3490&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e95a6830eba771de7657ec415c1a31b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba602c293552d3d1cc227f2fb935fe2c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6d9ce3f21c7d4f0447f68d282ddba6e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-66d79432cfb5da18b1aac0a6d772e676&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e3cde4a56707d1854488f0b25ff33596&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d94401800c111b74bf53e07ee0975662&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2747605a19dd90cae3b9e6a20d1194f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1405b111c59c1691a48901cde2eed51b</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
