    <node id="Hypertension">
      <data key="d0">Hypertension</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Hypertension is a chronic medical condition characterized by elevated blood pressure, documented in the patient's past medical history. As a pre-existing cardiovascular condition, hypertension represents a persistent elevation of arterial blood pressure that has been noted in the patient's medical records. This chronic condition is an important component of the patient's medical history and requires ongoing clinical attention and management as part of comprehensive healthcare assessment.&lt;SEP&gt;A chronic condition in the patient's past medical history characterized by elevated blood pressure.&lt;SEP&gt;High blood pressure condition documented in the patient's medical history.&lt;SEP&gt;A medical condition of elevated blood pressure in the patient's history.&lt;SEP&gt;Elevated blood pressure condition noted in the patient's past medical history.&lt;SEP&gt;A medical condition involving elevated blood pressure that was part of the patient's medical history.&lt;SEP&gt;Chronic condition in the patient's past medical history characterized by elevated blood pressure.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-571ddc4aa63fdf4b9d03942b5048b279&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-13a80dbd998d7aced4f85f4e332b3980&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0260e68b82e6826effdbcc686dec9cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1911d102d00d5197ec74e282f36fbad9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-51b315cb721376514a08823422d5c30f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6f98e594c48f4396c9da7f66fe58029d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4fd7d8854cca43bc54c0fae9bacd07a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d21fe1428431fa9900c5bdf9740d3490&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a1f1f43b5a8581949513cce1ff0ab8de&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7e52b6e535af5d46b5f2606e7f3ba818&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-903baf97d86d9b7dd49873c2407977ae&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-983b5f68059fc792b82433c7f0d17697&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-035214426d6755454aa9eb73b6e0d4e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fa5295eee150f6d2e5bed021b15fafd0</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
