    <node id="Ring-Enhancing Lesion">
      <data key="d0">Ring-Enhancing Lesion</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">An abnormal finding on MRI brain imaging showing a lesion with characteristic ring-like enhancement pattern.&lt;SEP&gt;An abnormal brain finding observed on MRI brain imaging, consistent with infection or inflammation.&lt;SEP&gt;A brain lesion with ring-shaped enhancement visible on MRI imaging, indicative of a pathological process in the patient's brain.&lt;SEP&gt;A radiological finding on MRI brain imaging characteristic of primary CNS lymphoma in the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;An abnormal finding on MRI brain imaging showing a lesion with ring-like enhancement characteristics.&lt;SEP&gt;A ring-enhancing lesion is an abnormal tissue growth visible on MRI brain imaging with characteristic ring-shaped contrast enhancement.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-571ddc4aa63fdf4b9d03942b5048b279&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1911d102d00d5197ec74e282f36fbad9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7f26c6d54ddb9d4b1f92d2f09061da7f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d94401800c111b74bf53e07ee0975662&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2747605a19dd90cae3b9e6a20d1194f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1405b111c59c1691a48901cde2eed51b</data>
