    <node id="Dexamethasone">
      <data key="d0">Dexamethasone</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Dexamethasone is a corticosteroid medication administered as part of patient treatment regimens. The primary function of dexamethasone within therapeutic protocols is to reduce inflammation and manage neurological symptoms associated with various patient conditions. As an anti-inflammatory agent, dexamethasone serves as a key component in addressing conditions that involve inflammatory processes and their associated neurological manifestations. Dexamethasone is typically administered alongside other medications as part of comprehensive treatment approaches, such as in combination with ceftriaxone in certain therapeutic protocols.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-571ddc4aa63fdf4b9d03942b5048b279&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a34ac93aa94bca40ac3bced0aa9de86&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4fd7d8854cca43bc54c0fae9bacd07a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d21fe1428431fa9900c5bdf9740d3490&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7e52b6e535af5d46b5f2606e7f3ba818&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-903baf97d86d9b7dd49873c2407977ae&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba602c293552d3d1cc227f2fb935fe2c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bbc516b53c71727bd08346a19ee50251&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a0808ea5951fe6ba96ffa3ee735cda17&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84e342b229c6a006856ecdc1a267768a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7f26c6d54ddb9d4b1f92d2f09061da7f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-66d79432cfb5da18b1aac0a6d772e676&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e3cde4a56707d1854488f0b25ff33596&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d94401800c111b74bf53e07ee0975662&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f3b72ae1dccac058d727442c28727b3d</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
