    <node id="Stable Neurological Deficit">
      <data key="d0">Stable Neurological Deficit</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">The patient's neurological condition remained stable at discharge following treatment.&lt;SEP&gt;The patient's neurological condition at discharge, indicating stabilization of neurological symptoms without deterioration.&lt;SEP&gt;The patient's clinical status at discharge showing stability despite persistent neurological deficits.</data>
