    <node id="Jaundice">
      <data key="d0">Jaundice</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Jaundice is a medical condition characterized by yellowing of the skin, eyes, and visible mucous membranes. This discoloration occurs as a result of elevated bilirubin levels in the bloodstream, which accumulate and deposit in these tissues, producing the characteristic yellow appearance.

The clinical presentation of jaundice in the described cases varies in duration, ranging from relatively short periods to extended presentations. Documentation indicates instances lasting 1 week, 3 weeks, 5 weeks (documented twice), 7 weeks, 10 weeks, and 14 weeks (documented twice) in different patients. This variability in duration reflects the diverse underlying causes and severity of jaundice across different clinical presentations, as the condition can result from various pathological processes affecting bilirubin metabolism, conjugation, or excretion.

The physical manifestations remain consistent across all cases, with yellowing of the skin and eyes being the primary observable signs. The extended durations documented in some cases suggest chronic or persistent hyperbilirubinemia requiring sustained clinical attention and investigation into the underlying etiology.&lt;SEP&gt;Jaundice is a clinical symptom characterized by yellowing of the skin and sclera, present for 28 weeks in the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;A medical condition characterized by yellowing of the skin and eyes, persisting for 28 weeks in the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;A medical condition characterized by yellowing of the skin and eyes, presenting in the patient with a duration of 28 weeks.&lt;SEP&gt;A condition of 28 weeks duration characterized by yellowing of the skin and sclera, associated with elevated liver enzymes and biliary obstruction.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-913dac86f1445586ee7313cee3abcef4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e0cf79a93d6937f4e196efd0a76b1c14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-552541f5707dbc91dc2b39f24da42ff3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-42c5dd7e4b8ae3efca148f8d10f468da&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d7dfbf9ae7bdd2da18160509a98a29b9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aea77867f87b397c2569ebf2e109e550&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3d50fc57a8c14c7819b2950816abc682&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-389cb396bf4e6268fa31af66e862032b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-93cc887c0186b2515e2821eabf31639d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-735be7666813a3f1eedf039a72df5db3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9bd68a770018591cf0e4611e9e14ae0c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d99b348010e0859bf79ca469b926378b</data>
