    <node id="Weight Loss">
      <data key="d0">Weight Loss</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">Weight Loss is a clinical symptom reported by the patient during their medical presentation. The patient experienced a loss of 8 kilograms, which occurred during the course of their illness and is considered indicative of systemic illness. This weight loss has been associated with multiple clinical conditions and presentations affecting the patient.

The weight loss was connected to a gastrointestinal condition and was accompanied by anorexia, contributing to the overall nutritional deficit. Additionally, the weight loss occurred alongside respiratory complaints as part of the patient's broader clinical symptomatology. The symptom was documented as part of the patient's comprehensive clinical presentation during the medical evaluation and assessment period.&lt;SEP&gt;A loss of 8 kg experienced by the patient as part of the clinical presentation.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-913dac86f1445586ee7313cee3abcef4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4fb8802354fa5826fc6a61e1d4703650&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-42c5dd7e4b8ae3efca148f8d10f468da&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d69e90de14f13f99bd017794598000f5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-389cb396bf4e6268fa31af66e862032b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aeb696350165bf9ae41216f5236c3817&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8ab7539afd48876f5bb300e184ed79b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1693a9d96722a090fabd3e1bd2ba20a2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-304f340ad4cf36f85eadeea2200b5890</data>
