    <node id="Dark Urine">
      <data key="d0">Dark Urine</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Dark Urine is a clinical symptom characterized by darkened or discolored urine observed in patients, typically indicating underlying hepatic or biliary dysfunction. This symptom serves as a significant clinical sign in medical assessment and diagnosis.

The darkening of urine in dark urine can result from various pathophysiological mechanisms. It may indicate the presence of bilirubinuria, where elevated levels of bilirubin are excreted in the urine due to liver dysfunction or impaired hepatic processing. Additionally, dark urine may suggest hematuria, the presence of blood or red blood cells in the urine. Both presentations represent potential markers of hepatic or biliary system compromise.

Dark urine is frequently associated with jaundice and biliary dysfunction, conditions that reflect disrupted bile metabolism and clearance. When observed as a clinical symptom, dark urine suggests potential hepatic dysfunction affecting the liver's capacity to properly metabolize and excrete bilirubin and other waste products. The appearance of darkened urine in a patient warrants clinical investigation to determine the underlying cause and assess the degree of liver or biliary system impairment.

As a clinical symptom, dark urine serves as an important diagnostic indicator prompting further evaluation for hepatic or biliary disorders. Healthcare providers recognize dark urine as a sign that requires investigation to identify whether the dysfunction originates from hepatic disease, biliary obstruction, or related conditions affecting bilirubin metabolism and excretion.&lt;SEP&gt;A symptom indicating possible liver dysfunction in the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;Dark urine is a symptom associated with the patient's rectal bleeding presentation.&lt;SEP&gt;A clinical symptom indicating impaired liver function and biliary obstruction.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-913dac86f1445586ee7313cee3abcef4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17baf644d96495d064f9649f631230b0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e0cf79a93d6937f4e196efd0a76b1c14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-552541f5707dbc91dc2b39f24da42ff3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-359c4bdb901dcb37d2cf0fa307a2c571&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0848622c01d4f566da1895987417746&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5efbbabff30dce7757a05e1d7b57eaa2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-93f288f93598c3b3a931faed20b2314c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3d50fc57a8c14c7819b2950816abc682&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17ee3298badd5c634297742f3bfdd8e4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d99b348010e0859bf79ca469b926378b</data>
