    <node id="Crohn's Disease">
      <data key="d0">Crohn's Disease</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Crohn's disease is an inflammatory bowel condition confirmed through liver biopsy of the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;An inflammatory bowel condition confirmed by liver biopsy in the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;An inflammatory bowel condition confirmed through liver biopsy in the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;Crohn's disease confirmed through liver biopsy.&lt;SEP&gt;Crohn's disease is an inflammatory bowel condition confirmed through liver biopsy findings in the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;An inflammatory bowel disease confirmed through liver biopsy in the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;An inflammatory bowel condition confirmed through liver biopsy in the patient.</data>
