    <node id="Gastrointestinal System">
      <data key="d0">Gastrointestinal System</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">The gastrointestinal system is the primary organ system affected in the clinical case under consideration. This biological system encompasses multiple anatomical structures, including the esophagus, colon, liver, and biliary tract. The gastrointestinal system has been formally designated as the primary system category for the patient's presenting condition and represents the central focus of clinical documentation and assessment.

The clinical presentation involves rectal bleeding and related complications affecting this system. The gastrointestinal system's involvement in the patient's condition is documented through case severity classification; however, severity assessments vary within the clinical documentation, with references to both low and medium severity levels. As the anatomical system primarily affected by the patient's clinical presentation, the gastrointestinal system serves as the key organ system involved in medical case evaluation and clinical decision-making processes.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-913dac86f1445586ee7313cee3abcef4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17baf644d96495d064f9649f631230b0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e0cf79a93d6937f4e196efd0a76b1c14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-552541f5707dbc91dc2b39f24da42ff3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-359c4bdb901dcb37d2cf0fa307a2c571&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0848622c01d4f566da1895987417746&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-299e0d28d253c37f9dddf4aef8eb2c94&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5efbbabff30dce7757a05e1d7b57eaa2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-93f288f93598c3b3a931faed20b2314c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4fb8802354fa5826fc6a61e1d4703650&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c6540caa7beb945f0321bf38942587d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-42c5dd7e4b8ae3efca148f8d10f468da&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d7dfbf9ae7bdd2da18160509a98a29b9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32a4845ff65651415af840aed5ad1767&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3d50fc57a8c14c7819b2950816abc682&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-caa60f44fc47125398c7ec53a5186865&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2af3da83b586005637f4530b60892346&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-12b0793fd5ff30936be7578fadb2f11c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-389cb396bf4e6268fa31af66e862032b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-93cc887c0186b2515e2821eabf31639d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17ee3298badd5c634297742f3bfdd8e4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd08cbda0f2618e783e7d18b1e718420&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9bd68a770018591cf0e4611e9e14ae0c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b832bffca6f5b953e97047ac37cd38ec&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dbdb6e100fb2bdb409feb08c479fa265&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d99b348010e0859bf79ca469b926378b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7f78e14c615a6efcb86bacdcef718021&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-304f340ad4cf36f85eadeea2200b5890&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1375b9b5b2e11625f9232d34b4107e38</data>
