    <node id="Dermatology Clinic">
      <data key="d0">Dermatology Clinic</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">The Dermatology Clinic is a specialized medical facility dedicated to the evaluation, diagnosis, and management of skin conditions and dermatological concerns. As a healthcare institution within the broader medical system, the clinic functions as a referral destination where patients are directed by other medical providers who recognize the need for specialized dermatological assessment and care.

The Dermatology Clinic serves as both a diagnostic and treatment center for various skin-related conditions. Patients are referred to the facility for comprehensive screening and detailed physical examination by dermatological specialists. The clinic conducts thorough clinical evaluations to assess suspicious or concerning skin lesions, including pigmented lesions that require professional assessment. These examinations are designed to determine the nature of skin abnormalities and establish appropriate diagnoses for identified conditions.

Beyond initial evaluation and diagnosis, the Dermatology Clinic is involved in the ongoing management and treatment of diagnosed skin conditions. The facility provides both diagnostic expertise and therapeutic interventions to address dermatological concerns identified during patient assessment. Through its comprehensive approach to dermatological care, the clinic plays a critical role in the diagnosis, evaluation, and long-term management of patients with various skin-related health issues.&lt;SEP&gt;A medical clinic specializing in dermatological care that evaluated and diagnosed the patient's skin condition.&lt;SEP&gt;A medical facility providing dermatological screening and treatment services.&lt;SEP&gt;A medical facility specializing in dermatology that evaluated and diagnosed the patient's skin condition.</data>
