      <data key="d0">Dyspnoea</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Progressive shortness of breath experienced by the patient over a 10-week period.&lt;SEP&gt;Progressive difficulty in breathing reported by the patient over a 3-week period prior to admission.&lt;SEP&gt;Progressive shortness of breath reported by the patient over a 2-week period.&lt;SEP&gt;Progressive shortness of breath reported by the patient with a 21-week history of development.</data>
