    <node id="Fatigue">
      <data key="d0">Fatigue</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Fatigue is a symptom reported by the patient as part of their clinical presentation and during admission. It manifests as persistent tiredness, exhaustion, and a general lack of energy that the patient experiences. The symptom is characterized by physical weakness and tiredness that the patient identifies as a notable aspect of their condition. Fatigue was reported alongside other clinical symptoms including dyspnoea and ankle swelling, indicating its presence within a broader symptomatology. Overall, fatigue represents a significant component of the patient's reported clinical symptoms, reflecting their subjective experience of exhaustion and diminished physical capacity.&lt;SEP&gt;Fatigue is a symptom of exhaustion reported by the patient during admission.&lt;SEP&gt;A symptom reported by the patient characterized by lack of energy and weakness.&lt;SEP&gt;Fatigue is a symptom reported by the patient indicating general weakness and exhaustion.&lt;SEP&gt;A symptom of reduced energy and exhaustion reported by the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;Fatigue is a symptom reported by the patient during admission.&lt;SEP&gt;A symptom reported by the patient indicating physical exhaustion.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-556d7ea1921560596bb0c596a00bdf0a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-937e867ddae2f8daaa79bd2e639976eb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3758214300d6bd794534d0e32e9bd057&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-92cc2c46c1f49338ed7955ea4238e60f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6c35da8135a5d590d4accdb1b51d149c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-11944cb5618b1905065e32d7424e5ea1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-27c41f1161752e203627b5fc920fca07&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b29acdc1599ff32318f1144aaa062a2b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-50c06f071bd4436025fb35de50515fda&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b77bea8599e47e5947ec3a7be0ce9b73&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b74bdb93da896529bce41ee41924095c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-11ac0d1d3c9697cf3ad1c05e8e52ee8a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dda6359792d27d913bf9dbba5833f91f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6c7f5f1efa9fe1ad162b412383e280bf</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1775169025</data>
      <data key="d6" />
