      <data key="d0">Mucosal Inflammation</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">Inflammation of airway mucosa observed during bronchoscopy examination.&lt;SEP&gt;Inflammation of the mucous membranes observed during bronchoscopy examination.&lt;SEP&gt;An inflammatory condition of the mucous membrane observed during bronchoscopy.&lt;SEP&gt;Mucosal inflammation is inflammation of the mucous membranes in the respiratory tract.&lt;SEP&gt;Mucosal inflammation is a finding from bronchoscopy indicating inflammation of the bronchial mucosa.</data>
