    <node id="Haemoptysis">
      <data key="d0">Haemoptysis</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Haemoptysis is a medical condition characterized by the coughing up of blood or blood-tinged sputum originating from the lungs. This condition presents as a primary symptom in various clinical contexts and can manifest over different durations.

In the documented cases, haemoptysis has been reported with varying temporal presentations. The condition was observed over periods ranging from 1 week to 28 weeks in duration. Specifically, instances of haemoptysis spanning 14 weeks appear in multiple clinical records, representing a prolonged presentation of this symptom. Additionally, cases with 7-week, 5-week, 1-week, and 28-week histories have been documented. The 1-week presentation occurred specifically prior to patient admission in one case.

Haemoptysis typically manifests as coughing or spitting of blood-stained or blood-tinged sputum and serves as a significant presenting symptom that often prompts clinical evaluation and hospital admission. The variability in duration among documented cases suggests that the symptom can present acutely over short periods or develop into a chronic manifestation persisting for several weeks, indicating diverse underlying etiologies and clinical trajectories.&lt;SEP&gt;A symptom characterized by coughing up blood, reported by the patient with a 21-week history.&lt;SEP&gt;Haemoptysis is a symptom characterized by coughing up blood, presenting with a 28-week duration in the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;Haemoptysis is the coughing up of blood, which the patient experienced over a 21-week period.&lt;SEP&gt;Haemoptysis is the coughing up of blood, reported by the patient for 5 weeks prior to admission.&lt;SEP&gt;A symptom characterized by coughing up blood, reported by the patient over a 10-week period.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-937e867ddae2f8daaa79bd2e639976eb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-348a6f93e1df4665db6794f8f475315a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf05a1180370ca5c22ffbfcdb89ab2d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e7f38ad205281fc2b3d3fdc52c5a8b5c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-74df9a5aaec0ab322e9634e2a357e4ae&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-680b0868e00cfb2dc1ba062d72742486&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b29acdc1599ff32318f1144aaa062a2b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-50c06f071bd4436025fb35de50515fda&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b77bea8599e47e5947ec3a7be0ce9b73&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b74bdb93da896529bce41ee41924095c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ef20424effc0d32c39fcdcec5da83d2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6c4cc1d83b1ff0beb41c0996e0bed59f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4f335b1b7bae18006bc038ab4128db1</data>
