    <node id="Wheeze">
      <data key="d0">Wheeze</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Wheeze is a respiratory symptom characterized by high-pitched whistling sounds detected during breathing. It manifests as an abnormal breathing sound that is both audible to clinicians during physical examination through chest auscultation and reported by patients as a subjective symptom of disrupted airflow. The presence of wheeze serves as a key clinical finding that helps guide diagnostic assessment and treatment decisions.

Wheeze indicates underlying airway obstruction or inflammation within the respiratory tract. The symptom can be associated with various clinical conditions, including foreign body aspiration, which presents as an identifiable abnormal breathing sound during physical examination. In some cases, wheeze may be detected bilaterally, indicating involvement across both sides of the chest. The whistling sound results from disrupted airflow through narrowed or obstructed airways during the breathing process.

During clinical evaluation, wheeze is detected through auscultation of the chest, where it serves as an important diagnostic indicator reflecting disruption of normal airflow patterns through the airways. This objective finding, combined with patient-reported descriptions of the abnormal breathing sounds, helps clinicians identify potential airway pathology and guides further diagnostic investigation. Wheeze may appear as part of a patient's clinical presentation over specific timeframes, such as within a 28-day clinical history, and remains a significant respiratory symptom in clinical assessment protocols.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-3d29c25e21e325edd849f3dc97bf8a04&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf05a1180370ca5c22ffbfcdb89ab2d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d5bcc445de13e0cbc298cdc386c5d44&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-74df9a5aaec0ab322e9634e2a357e4ae&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9d8c12fa6d02482beb80341b410dc4fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2fe603f70880276dc53d591b2c6fc6ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-680b0868e00cfb2dc1ba062d72742486&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-edefebc0c0ccf297dd9120097036b554&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cd85436604dc21edf42918a59c026df6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-11ac0d1d3c9697cf3ad1c05e8e52ee8a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea49e51c9a44c10ef5253c942a3bd509&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-125eccf021b8ac36d38facc6f2707698&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ebdec2fe609dbeb73244f6c370f4d8eb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6c7f5f1efa9fe1ad162b412383e280bf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5211c9d4452573a55519727c0ef76b1</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
