    </node>
    <node id="Community-Acquired Pneumonia">
      <data key="d0">Community-Acquired Pneumonia</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Community-acquired pneumonia is the diagnosis established for the patient based on clinical presentation and diagnostic findings.&lt;SEP&gt;The established diagnosis of pneumonia acquired outside of hospital settings.&lt;SEP&gt;The diagnosis established for the patient based on clinical presentation and diagnostic findings.&lt;SEP&gt;Community-acquired pneumonia is the diagnosis established for the patient after clinical and diagnostic evaluation.&lt;SEP&gt;The diagnosis established for the patient indicating lung infection acquired outside a hospital setting.&lt;SEP&gt;The diagnosed condition affecting the patient, characterized by respiratory infection acquired outside a hospital setting.&lt;SEP&gt;The established diagnosis for the patient indicating lung infection acquired outside hospital settings.</data>
