    <node id="Haemorrhagic Transformation">
      <data key="d0">Haemorrhagic Transformation</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">A finding on MRI brain showing bleeding or hemorrhagic changes in cerebral tissue.&lt;SEP&gt;Finding on MRI brain imaging indicating bleeding or hemorrhagic changes in the brain.&lt;SEP&gt;A condition involving bleeding in the brain, identified through MRI imaging of the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;A condition revealed on MRI brain imaging showing bleeding in the brain tissue.&lt;SEP&gt;A condition identified on MRI brain imaging, indicating conversion of ischaemic stroke to haemorrhagic stroke.&lt;SEP&gt;Bleeding in the brain identified on MRI imaging of the patient.</data>
