    <node id="Nocturnal Pain">
      <data key="d0">Nocturnal Pain</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Pain occurring during nighttime hours that was associated with the patient's joint symptoms over a 14-month duration.&lt;SEP&gt;Pain experienced by the patient during nighttime hours, associated with the knee condition.&lt;SEP&gt;Nocturnal pain is pain occurring during nighttime hours, a symptom associated with the patient's wrist and MCP involvement.&lt;SEP&gt;Nocturnal pain associated with shoulder stiffness is a key symptom affecting the patient's nighttime comfort.&lt;SEP&gt;Pain occurring at night, an associated symptom affecting the patient's shoulder region.&lt;SEP&gt;Pain occurring at night experienced by the patient associated with spine involvement.&lt;SEP&gt;Pain experienced by the patient during nighttime, associated with the knee condition.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-dc908789d613380f6cd7ce177b5dfafb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-47645b674af4f2a88a64e49657a83073&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c1de22df34c77d7bc601fa40ded28a01&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a667de4da28bb439da82a6fd3153ca1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1367d2b19d4c80169f6e3f681823cd2c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b2c623dc26c99ebd3a6caf0a7b69babb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-996a573759ff4451282c4bad9069e599</data>
