    <node id="Atrial Fibrillation">
      <data key="d0">Atrial Fibrillation</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Atrial fibrillation is a cardiac arrhythmia characterized by an irregular heart rhythm resulting from abnormal electrical activity in the heart. This condition was diagnosed in the patient through electrocardiogram (ECG) examination, which revealed the irregular atrial contractions and abnormal cardiac electrical activity characteristic of the disease.

In this patient's case, the atrial fibrillation was identified as new-onset, indicating a recent development of the condition rather than a longstanding or chronic arrhythmia. The condition forms an important part of the patient's documented medical history.

The management of atrial fibrillation in this patient involves anticoagulation therapy, which is a critical treatment approach for this condition. Anticoagulation treatment is employed to reduce the patient's risk of thromboembolic complications, particularly stroke, which are significant clinical concerns associated with atrial fibrillation. The irregular heart rhythm characteristic of atrial fibrillation can promote blood clot formation within the cardiac chambers, thereby increasing the risk of systemic thromboembolism. By administering anticoagulation therapy, the risk of these potentially life-threatening complications is mitigated, making this treatment an essential component of the patient's overall cardiac management strategy.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-8a6870a0ae60e5e97ee38192a8c7cb33&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c23e378760ce2cf115e65e9075717448&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9953fc82aa24f3592983321f1a24638a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-51b315cb721376514a08823422d5c30f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e95a6830eba771de7657ec415c1a31b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bbc516b53c71727bd08346a19ee50251&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-af28652606d78849d0249d790f40681f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6bd187f61bb50ddf67fed66dbf47414b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4004490c7f995b8c84484a113ba933ec&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a0808ea5951fe6ba96ffa3ee735cda17&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84e342b229c6a006856ecdc1a267768a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b934702b442931687944c3b680751df6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2747605a19dd90cae3b9e6a20d1194f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1405b111c59c1691a48901cde2eed51b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-15f9eef500fedf61aecc494b64b11664</data>
