    <node id="Reduced Range of Motion">
      <data key="d0">Reduced Range of Motion</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">A symptom affecting the patient's spine, indicating limited joint mobility.&lt;SEP&gt;Reduced range of motion affecting the spine is the primary symptom presented by the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;A symptom affecting the knee joint, limiting the patient's ability to move the joint through its full range.&lt;SEP&gt;A symptom affecting the wrist and MCPs, indicating joint movement limitation in the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;Reduced range of motion in the hip is a primary clinical presentation symptom in the patient.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-91f2e17beb9f3d24b9faa9059ed6acae&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d5ef4a9ff207d5fcf312fa4948419500&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-996a573759ff4451282c4bad9069e599&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c81af782e89b002c04a944dc0cea584&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-606a0358ec61458bc198d5e4d438844f</data>
