    <node id="Low-Dose Prednisolone">
      <data key="d0">Low-Dose Prednisolone</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Low-dose prednisolone is a corticosteroid medication administered to patients as part of their clinical management and treatment regimens. This medication is utilized across multiple therapeutic contexts to address various inflammatory and autoimmune conditions.

Low-dose prednisolone is employed in the management of osteoarthritis, where it serves to control inflammation and associated symptoms. Additionally, the medication is used in the treatment of gout, helping to manage the inflammatory response characteristic of this condition. In the context of systemic lupus erythematosus (SLE), low-dose prednisolone is incorporated into the management plan to address the systemic inflammatory manifestations of this autoimmune disorder.

The primary function of low-dose prednisolone across these conditions is to manage inflammation and alleviate symptoms associated with the patient's underlying condition. As a corticosteroid, it works by suppressing inflammatory responses, making it a valuable component of comprehensive treatment regimens for various musculoskeletal and systemic conditions. The medication is administered as part of a broader management plan tailored to the individual patient's clinical needs and diagnosis.&lt;SEP&gt;Low-dose prednisolone is a corticosteroid medication used in the treatment of rheumatoid arthritis for this patient.&lt;SEP&gt;A corticosteroid medication administered at low doses as part of the rheumatoid arthritis management regimen.&lt;SEP&gt;A corticosteroid medication used in the management of the patient's condition.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-c49c05a874ce6761c157c4e35dd9903b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6f3968a1e0f64443d559f9c75594cad0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5da01a385b47958d437c2b60db9a3505&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-05e39d703a228f9f75806162f2ec5ed2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-47645b674af4f2a88a64e49657a83073&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a667de4da28bb439da82a6fd3153ca1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-858effb6f3bd62fa4b2171b7a13e1257&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1367d2b19d4c80169f6e3f681823cd2c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d5688d8714c141858552becb5c4be710&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d745ec6e17e6c423c81b61841434f2ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f0cb44df10264318173904dd8b4a1b9e</data>
