    <node id="Palpitations">
      <data key="d0">Palpitations</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Palpitations are a symptom characterized by an abnormal or heightened awareness of heartbeats, which may be experienced as irregular or forceful cardiac sensations. This symptom manifests as the patient's conscious perception of their own heartbeat, which normally occurs below the threshold of awareness.

In the case presented, the patient experienced palpitations for varying durations prior to presentation. The documented timelines range from a brief 2-day period immediately preceding emergency department presentation to more prolonged episodes extending up to 28 days prior to seeking medical care. Specifically, the patient reported palpitation episodes lasting 5 days on multiple occasions, a 10-day period of abnormal heartbeat awareness, a 21-day duration documented on two separate instances, and a more extended 28-day episode of irregular or forceful heartbeats. These varying durations suggest either multiple distinct episodes of palpitations occurring at different times, or a protracted symptomatic period with fluctuations in severity or patient awareness.

The palpitations were characterized by both the sensation of awareness of heartbeats and descriptions of abnormal or irregular heartbeat patterns. The symptom prompted the patient to seek emergency medical evaluation, indicating a level of concern or symptom severity warranting acute clinical assessment. The range of durations—from acute (2 days) to subacute or chronic presentations (up to 28 days)—suggests that palpitations in this patient represented a significant clinical concern requiring medical intervention and evaluation for potential underlying cardiac pathology or arrhythmia.&lt;SEP&gt;Symptom experienced by the patient characterized by a 14-day history of abnormal heart sensations.&lt;SEP&gt;A symptom experienced by the patient characterized by an awareness of rapid or irregular heartbeat lasting one day.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-c23e378760ce2cf115e65e9075717448&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2a418de55ab776ed3382840643ce211c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0260e68b82e6826effdbcc686dec9cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-48d485c49b8fecae90419b536e5c22d5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a1f1f43b5a8581949513cce1ff0ab8de&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-983b5f68059fc792b82433c7f0d17697&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-da9725a3a120031d9b91eb87eeb7ea97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4004490c7f995b8c84484a113ba933ec&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fa5295eee150f6d2e5bed021b15fafd0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-205b75d592f5c35757c06b25aa8e1984</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1775169209</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
