    <node id="Paediatric Emergency Department">
      <data key="d0">Paediatric Emergency Department</data>
      <data key="d1">location</data>
      <data key="d2">The Paediatric Emergency Department is a specialized medical facility designed to provide emergency evaluation, treatment, and care for pediatric patients. This healthcare facility is specifically equipped to handle pediatric critical cases and serves as the destination where children are brought by parents or caregivers during medical emergencies. The department functions as a comprehensive emergency care environment where young patients receive prompt assessment, diagnostic evaluation, and appropriate medical treatment in response to acute health conditions. The Paediatric Emergency Department represents a crucial component of pediatric healthcare infrastructure, dedicated to managing emergency situations involving children and providing the specialized expertise and resources necessary for pediatric emergency medicine.&lt;SEP&gt;The paediatric emergency department is the healthcare facility where the patient was brought for emergency evaluation and treatment.&lt;SEP&gt;The medical facility where the patient was brought for evaluation and treatment of critical symptoms.&lt;SEP&gt;The medical facility where the patient was brought for emergency treatment.&lt;SEP&gt;The paediatric emergency department where the patient was brought for evaluation and treatment.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-6d5bcc445de13e0cbc298cdc386c5d44&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-633b98afe9675d274497d13c770dc7a8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-664a546642468c69e4060dadf0cf6259&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9d8c12fa6d02482beb80341b410dc4fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2fe603f70880276dc53d591b2c6fc6ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-edefebc0c0ccf297dd9120097036b554&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cd85436604dc21edf42918a59c026df6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8eff0da2c4db4508c02bd09795c327d2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea49e51c9a44c10ef5253c942a3bd509&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-125eccf021b8ac36d38facc6f2707698&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cb2cd72190b2ba60ab4d0ac08898df5c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5211c9d4452573a55519727c0ef76b1</data>
