    <node id="Neurological Examination">
      <data key="d0">Neurological Examination</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">Neurological Examination

The neurological examination is a physical and clinical assessment procedure performed to evaluate a patient's neurological function and status. This systematic clinical assessment is designed to identify and document focal neurological findings and abnormalities in the patient's nervous system.

In the cases described, the neurological examination revealed multiple significant findings. The patient demonstrated left-sided hemiplegia (paralysis affecting the left side of the body) and dysphasia (difficulty with speech or language comprehension). Additionally, the examination identified papilloedema (swelling of the optic disc), cranial nerve palsy (dysfunction of one or more cranial nerves), positive Kernig's sign (a clinical indicator often associated with meningeal irritation), and hyperreflexia (exaggerated or overactive reflexes). These diverse findings indicate a comprehensive neurological assessment that systematically evaluated motor function, language function, cranial nerve integrity, meningeal signs, and reflex responses.

The neurological examination serves as a fundamental diagnostic tool in clinical practice, enabling healthcare providers to localize neurological lesions, assess the severity of neurological dysfunction, and guide further diagnostic investigation and treatment planning based on the specific abnormalities detected.&lt;SEP&gt;A clinical assessment performed to evaluate neurological function and identify right facial droop and hyperreflexia.&lt;SEP&gt;A clinical assessment procedure performed on the patient to evaluate neurological function and identify abnormalities.&lt;SEP&gt;Clinical assessment performed to identify neurological findings including hemiplegia and hyperreflexia in the patient.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-ce7467c36645566972e9f92c5fea2ee8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c3052227d42277d8826362c90a01ca5a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-035214426d6755454aa9eb73b6e0d4e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bbc516b53c71727bd08346a19ee50251&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-df174d639a33c9effb2f0ce6df80ce71&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a0808ea5951fe6ba96ffa3ee735cda17&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e3cde4a56707d1854488f0b25ff33596&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d94401800c111b74bf53e07ee0975662&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b934702b442931687944c3b680751df6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2747605a19dd90cae3b9e6a20d1194f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f3b72ae1dccac058d727442c28727b3d</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
