      <data key="d2">A clinical finding on physical examination showing decreased airflow on one side of the chest.&lt;SEP&gt;A physical examination finding indicating reduced air entry on one side of the patient's chest.&lt;SEP&gt;Unilateral reduced air entry is a clinical finding observed on physical examination.&lt;SEP&gt;A clinical finding during examination indicating reduced air movement on one side of the chest.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-664a546642468c69e4060dadf0cf6259&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9d8c12fa6d02482beb80341b410dc4fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cd85436604dc21edf42918a59c026df6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cb2cd72190b2ba60ab4d0ac08898df5c</data>
