    <node id="Photophobia">
      <data key="d0">Photophobia</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Photophobia is a neurological symptom involving sensitivity to light, presented by the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;A symptom involving sensitivity to light, presented as part of the patient's neurological condition.&lt;SEP&gt;Symptom involving sensitivity to light, occurring alongside focal weakness in the patient's presentation.&lt;SEP&gt;Light sensitivity experienced by the patient as a presenting symptom.&lt;SEP&gt;Light sensitivity symptom presenting as part of the patient's acute neurological condition.&lt;SEP&gt;Sensitivity to light experienced by the patient as a presenting symptom.&lt;SEP&gt;Symptom of light sensitivity presented by the patient alongside focal weakness.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-d4fd7d8854cca43bc54c0fae9bacd07a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d21fe1428431fa9900c5bdf9740d3490&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e95a6830eba771de7657ec415c1a31b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6d9ce3f21c7d4f0447f68d282ddba6e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-df174d639a33c9effb2f0ce6df80ce71&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-66d79432cfb5da18b1aac0a6d772e676&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e3cde4a56707d1854488f0b25ff33596</data>
