      <data key="d3">chunk-9e95a6830eba771de7657ec415c1a31b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bbc516b53c71727bd08346a19ee50251&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6bd187f61bb50ddf67fed66dbf47414b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b934702b442931687944c3b680751df6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1405b111c59c1691a48901cde2eed51b</data>
      <data key="d2">The patient's atrial fibrillation was managed with anticoagulation therapy.&lt;SEP&gt;A therapeutic approach used to manage the patient's atrial fibrillation.&lt;SEP&gt;A therapeutic approach used to treat the patient's atrial fibrillation by preventing blood clot formation.&lt;SEP&gt;A therapeutic approach used to treat the patient's atrial fibrillation and prevent thromboembolic complications.&lt;SEP&gt;Anticoagulation is a treatment method using medications to prevent blood clot formation in patients with atrial fibrillation.</data>
