    <node id="Hyperreflexia">
      <data key="d0">Hyperreflexia</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Hyperreflexia is an abnormal neurological finding characterized by exaggerated or increased reflex responses. The condition is detected and diagnosed during a patient's neurological examination, where healthcare providers observe and assess the intensity and speed of reflex reactions to stimuli. Hyperreflexia represents a deviation from normal reflex behavior, indicating heightened or amplified responses compared to expected physiological standards. This finding can serve as an important clinical indicator of underlying neurological conditions or abnormalities affecting the nervous system's reflex arc pathway.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-7e52b6e535af5d46b5f2606e7f3ba818&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-903baf97d86d9b7dd49873c2407977ae&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba602c293552d3d1cc227f2fb935fe2c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6d9ce3f21c7d4f0447f68d282ddba6e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6bd187f61bb50ddf67fed66dbf47414b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d94401800c111b74bf53e07ee0975662&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b934702b442931687944c3b680751df6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f3b72ae1dccac058d727442c28727b3d</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1775169191</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Whole-Brain Radiotherapy">
      <data key="d0">Whole-Brain Radiotherapy</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">A therapeutic treatment modality involving radiation to the entire brain, administered to the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;A cancer treatment approach involving radiation to the entire brain, administered to the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;A radiation therapy treatment applied to the entire brain as part of the patient's therapeutic intervention.&lt;SEP&gt;Radiation therapy applied to the entire brain as part of the treatment regimen for the patient.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-7e52b6e535af5d46b5f2606e7f3ba818&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-903baf97d86d9b7dd49873c2407977ae&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7f26c6d54ddb9d4b1f92d2f09061da7f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f3b72ae1dccac058d727442c28727b3d</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1775169191</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
