    <edge source="CT Abdomen" target="Circumferential Colonic Thickening">
      <data key="d7">8.0</data>
      <data key="d8">CT Abdomen with Circumferential Colonic Thickening represents a radiological finding identified through computed tomography imaging of the abdomen. This relation describes the diagnostic detection and visualization of circumferential thickening of the colon wall as observed on CT abdomen imaging studies.

The relation indicates that CT abdomen imaging serves as the diagnostic modality through which circumferential colonic thickening is revealed and identified in patients. Circumferential colonic thickening, characterized by uniform thickening of the colon wall that extends around the entire circumference of the organ, appears as a significant diagnostic finding on CT abdomen imaging. This radiological finding is detected through careful examination of the abdominal CT scans and is documented as an important clinical observation during imaging interpretation.

The relation establishes that CT abdomen imaging is utilized to detect, visualize, and characterize circumferential colonic thickening in patients' colons. The presence of circumferential colonic thickening on CT abdomen imaging constitutes a notable diagnostic finding that may indicate various underlying pathological conditions affecting the colonic wall, warranting further clinical correlation and investigation. This imaging finding and its detection through CT abdomen imaging represent a key component of radiological assessment and diagnostic evaluation in clinical practice.</data>
      <data key="d9">diagnostic discovery,diagnostic finding,diagnostic procedure,finding detection,imaging finding,imaging modality,imaging procedure,imaging study,radiological finding,structural abnormality</data>
      <data key="d10">chunk-b0848622c01d4f566da1895987417746&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-299e0d28d253c37f9dddf4aef8eb2c94&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4fb8802354fa5826fc6a61e1d4703650&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32a4845ff65651415af840aed5ad1767&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aea77867f87b397c2569ebf2e109e550&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17ee3298badd5c634297742f3bfdd8e4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd08cbda0f2618e783e7d18b1e718420&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b832bffca6f5b953e97047ac37cd38ec</data>
