    <edge source="Pulmonary Function Tests" target="Mixed Pattern">
      <data key="d7">10.0</data>
      <data key="d8">Mixed Pattern, Pulmonary Function Tests refers to a clinical finding identified through pulmonary function testing in which a patient exhibits a combined pattern of both obstructive and restrictive lung dysfunction. This mixed pattern represents a simultaneous presence of abnormalities in respiratory function, indicating that the patient's lungs demonstrate characteristics of both obstructive airway disease and restrictive lung disease.

In this condition, pulmonary function tests reveal respiratory impairment that is neither purely obstructive nor purely restrictive in nature, but rather a combination of both pathophysiological mechanisms affecting lung function. The mixed pattern of respiratory dysfunction or abnormality indicates compromise in the patient's overall pulmonary capacity and gas exchange mechanisms, reflecting a more complex underlying pathology than what would be observed with a single obstructive or restrictive pattern alone.

This finding is clinically significant as it suggests multiple processes affecting the lungs simultaneously, which may result from various etiologies including concurrent obstructive and restrictive diseases, advanced stages of primary lung disease, or secondary effects of systemic conditions on pulmonary function. The identification of a mixed pattern through pulmonary function testing is important for guiding clinical management and understanding the multifaceted nature of the patient's respiratory impairment.&lt;SEP&gt;Pulmonary function tests indicated a mixed pattern of pulmonary dysfunction.&lt;SEP&gt;Pulmonary function tests indicated a mixed pattern in the patient's lung function.</data>
      <data key="d9">diagnostic finding,diagnostic method,diagnostic test result,functional assessment,functional finding,pulmonary dysfunction,respiratory assessment,respiratory dysfunction,test finding,test result</data>
      <data key="d10">chunk-3758214300d6bd794534d0e32e9bd057&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-92cc2c46c1f49338ed7955ea4238e60f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e7f38ad205281fc2b3d3fdc52c5a8b5c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b29acdc1599ff32318f1144aaa062a2b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-50c06f071bd4436025fb35de50515fda&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b77bea8599e47e5947ec3a7be0ce9b73&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3fa76722cb250ebdc3971241f8d1d7a1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aeb696350165bf9ae41216f5236c3817&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8ab7539afd48876f5bb300e184ed79b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4f335b1b7bae18006bc038ab4128db1</data>
